<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c4">[المحكَّم]</span>: المجرّب.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>... و <span class="c4">[مفعِّل]</span>، بكسر العين<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
